    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "An appropriation of $4,000 was\nmade by the city council last night\nfor the extension of new water\nmains on the north hill, for the re-\nlief of the Kenwood-L idgerwood\ndistrict and the region west of Di-\nvision that draws its water supply\nfrom the new North Side force\nmain.\n\n\nThe plan Is to run new supply\nmains on Division and Cincinnati\nstreets almost to the north city linn\nits, and also to replace certain\nwooden mains and small mains in\nthat region that are now incapable\nof withstanding the high pressure\nthat it is expected will be present"
    }
